## Other Software/Firmware Components Relevant This Release

This CIU firmware file is intended to be used by the NGI-5000 Logic Module

## Load/Install/Update Instructions:

* Use the update manager on the NGI-5000 configuration tool to install the NGI-5000 CIU firmware.

